{"tid":480190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反社會人格既上到位，真係好可怕】","createTime":"2017-11-26T01:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T00:35:07.000Z","uid":29314,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0016a736287dfad54420922188a48289ed9c4502","tid":480190,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:22:39.000Z","msg":"施永青，本地地產經紀龍頭公司創辦人。<br />\n<br />\n香港地產經紀公司係寡頭壟斷生意，大行得兩三間，行業無外來競爭。係人都知香港咁多年獨沽一味靠地產，呢十幾年樓市仲要熱到啪啪聲，的確，施生係資本主義社會好成功* (a.k.a. 發左幾次達)。<br />\n<br />\n呢個人，講過農曆年唔會同人講「恭喜發財」*；又因為細個家貧，循環再用聖誕卡畀同學仔恥笑，而最憎聖誕節**。佢話呢D叫我行我素，我就覺得呢個人因為出身寒微（佢自己好proud of 呢一點，窮人出身可以襯托出佢而家幾叻），畀人恰得多，有童年陰影，從而有反節日既心態。<br />\n<br />\n呢個人，為左自己同一眾地產商既利益，公開話地球沒有環保需要***，大力支持係郊野公園起樓。<br />\n<br />\n最新出爐，就話咁多小學生有抑鬱，唔係因為社會畀時下細路既壓力太大，而係因為佢地對社會有美好幻想****。<br />\n<br />\n呢個人，為左增加自己係社會既影響力，幫金主發聲，創辦免費報紙，自己日日寫專欄月旦時事。佢聲稱自己唔鐘意應酬，但又經常係大小論壇現身做，想畀人口齒伶俐、能言善辯，有魅力既形象。<br />\n<br />\n不過，大家應該唔難發現，施生思維缺乏同理心，為求達到目的會不擇手段，赤裸裸為利益利用別人，傷害別人後卻沒有一絲內疚感。<br />\n<br />\n呢d，叫「反社會人格障礙」（Antisocial personality disorder）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同步連載，岩睇既請like and share：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/WestRiceGoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWestRiceGoo&d=3WmJyH6EkxGsGwayycMgSC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e68e64c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/WestRiceGoo</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/westricegoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fwestricegoo&d=3WmJyH6EkxGsGwayycMgSC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=33956ddd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.instagram.com/westricegoo</a><br />\n<br />\n註：<br />\n* 2008年6月13日，am730 「C觀點」專欄<br />\n** 2012年12月18日，壹週刊訪問。<br />\n*** 2017年1月24日，am730「C觀點」專欄<br />\n**** 2017年11月23日，am730「C觀點」專欄<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/26/092220_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F26%2F092220_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=b36d3dbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85ef2aef2eebd72067a53e28950e4e7d79c228e0","tid":480190,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71047bb880a75d556a90fc0100f91e9e0708676f","tid":480190,"uid":49197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:41:56.000Z","msg":"成王 敗寇"},{"pid":"0a7112bb78e748d2232afab14e00f74f250446be","tid":480190,"uid":14482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:44:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a7e8c30d69d835b06884799f1c793eb2b35839b","tid":480190,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:48:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成王 敗寇</blockquote><br />\n你識野</blockquote><br />\n佢都算「成王」？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只係依附係一眾大媽沙身邊既寄生蟲je"},{"pid":"994ff4da5bbdb385b89a04889b7408726afebcc2","tid":480190,"uid":22858,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T03:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://whatscap.ristury.com/java/WhatsCAP/content/photo/v1/65_WM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhatscap.ristury.com%2Fjava%2FWhatsCAP%2Fcontent%2Fphoto%2Fv1%2F65_WM.jpg&h=64ca0115&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7243858bcb66b62a7f8cee154c7914c4bf3d1047","tid":480190,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:23:01.000Z","msg":"創世紀個許文彪咪就係影射呢d人囉"},{"pid":"7144667945dff97236af31aa899e8b37952b3bde","tid":480190,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:26:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec6cc68f19d148d87653ac230b227dd6892a22f5","tid":480190,"uid":5734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T10:58:21.000Z","msg":"心理追兇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced448477cb43442990f912fc229d5a063fee7fa","tid":480190,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc85b5f3a9a62e01ef6e2244d663cc04f93140a3","tid":480190,"uid":6435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:05:26.000Z","msg":"香港人比較崇拜呢種人"},{"pid":"160194a7e336d8e11c12ba2fef504866aae9a7e2","tid":480190,"uid":53429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7416ae75ca0a035e3be589a8c6c2684517bb1538","tid":480190,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/54/4e/84/544e84e4f2378736bfd90e0ff1b44611.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F54%2F4e%2F84%2F544e84e4f2378736bfd90e0ff1b44611.jpg&h=3bf5f331&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e00516cfc9cd7117a99057aabf9063c156e356a3","tid":480190,"uid":96743,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:15:09.000Z","msg":"呢個人，講過農曆年唔會同人講「恭喜發財」*；又因為細個家貧，循環再用聖誕卡畀同學仔恥笑，而最憎聖誕節**。佢話呢D叫我行我素，我就覺得呢個人因為出身寒微（佢自己好proud of 呢一點，窮人出身可以襯托出佢而家幾叻），畀人恰得多，有童年陰影，從而有反節日既心態。<br />\n<br />\n你打斷野都好武斷下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔鐘意過時過節慶祝節日<br />\n因為我覺得呢d係商家佬陰謀<br />\n咁樣我又有反社會人格障礙<br />\n再者你一個佢反社會既例子都無<br />\n例如佢為左上位要逼阿邊個邊個去死<br />\n做左d咩陰質野呃人錢咁<br />\n你咁樣講話佢性無能都得啦"},{"pid":"839e39e9985538e77155312e02c52e6df4a9215d","tid":480190,"uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T12:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個人，講過農曆年唔會同人講「恭喜發財」*；又因為細個家貧，循環再用聖誕卡畀同學仔恥笑，而最憎聖誕節**。佢話呢D叫我行我素，我就覺得呢個人因為出身寒微（佢自己好proud of 呢一點，窮人出身可以襯托出佢而家幾叻），畀人恰得多，有童年陰影，從而有反節日既心態。<br />\n<br />\n你打斷野都好武斷下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔鐘意過時過節慶祝節日<br />\n因為我覺得呢d係商家佬陰謀<br />\n咁樣我又有反社會人格障礙<br />\n再者你一個佢反社會既例子都無<br />\n例如佢為左上位要逼阿邊個邊個去死<br />\n做左d咩陰質野呃人錢咁<br />\n你咁樣講話佢性無能都得啦</blockquote><br />\n咁你應該睇返佢點解唔鐘意過節。<br />\n<br />\n並唔係因為佢討厭節日物質化or商家佬騎劫個節日or佢唔信教"},{"pid":"7845cc0ad4e1e6f0c79ed90d7897cd692b02e708","tid":480190,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T23:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf5fbefa64df15466385d4ce37924c556b33c39","tid":480190,"uid":29804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T00:10:05.000Z","msg":"佢係性格扭曲"},{"pid":"6435155270766a351264361945f48414a4345602","tid":480190,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T00:13:03.000Z","msg":"睇左佢怪責小朋友既專欄<br />\n<br />\n仲講咩自己細個冇得食牛雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73bac44e53cb8267ff72ab2cd1bfbab45a5c1da6","tid":480190,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T00:15:18.000Z","msg":"刻薄啫，佢不知幾想社會穩定"},{"pid":"b1d0abc0622820a78108142e6e2bf539d103457f","tid":480190,"uid":48680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T00:17:42.000Z","msg":"如果佢咁既人橫行無忌<br />\n咁香港咪係一個反社會人既社會lor<br />\n<br />\n乜你覺得比呢班蛋散攪成咁既香港<br />\n仲有資格做一個 社會咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n稱返佢做分層人類養殖場啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7ef236f836ffbf14b17a03783ed3fae43444cf","tid":480190,"uid":57848,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T00:35:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>刻薄啫，佢不知幾想社會穩定</blockquote><br />\n反社會唔代表要顛覆社會，而係個人冇同理心，就算傷害人都冇感覺，呢類人好多時都會skip咗前因後果話某啲人抵死唔抵可憐，或者傷害人仲話自己係對佢好。<br />\n<br />\n屍生篇文咁講，完全係曲線話自己成功全靠自己捱得姐，其實冇咩反社會影子。佢都話係個社會教到佢地太易成功姐。"}]}